'''Club Deportivo Filanbanco''' was a football team based out of [[Guayaquil]], [[Ecuador]]. It was formed in 1979 by [[Filanbanco]], one of the largest banks in Ecuador. The club dissolved a little after one decade of existence when it ceded its team to [[Valdez Sporting Club]]. It was the [[Serie A de Ecuador|Serie A]] runner-up in 1987.
