'''Erzurum BB GSK''', short for '''Erzurum Büyükşehir Belediyesi Gençlik Spor Kulübü''', is the [[ice hockey]] team of the same named [[multi-sport]] club in [[Erzurum]], Turkey founded by the metropolitan municipality ({{lang-tr|Büyükşehir Belediyesi}}). Currently, the team compete in the [[Turkish Ice Hockey Super League]] (TBHSL).
